posting_body: ['Property Address', '658 Grand Ave - B | St. Paul, MN 55105', 'Available:', '09/01/2022', 'Offered By', 'At Home Apartments', 'Description', 'Charming 1 Bedroom Located at Grand Tavern Flats', 'This top-floor, one-bedroom apartment includes charming historic features such as hardwood floors, arched doorways, and original built-in cabinetry.', 'Granite counters in the kitchen give an updated feel.', 'Enjoy this prime location on Grand Avenue.', 'Find yourself living in a beautiful, sunny apartment above the Tavern on Grand in the best area the city has to offer.', 'The perfect mix of character and convenience are at your doorstep when you are living on Grand Avenue!', 'Residents have included access to the clubhouse and fitness center just over one mile away!', 'Unlimited, coinless laundry on-site for a flat monthly fee.', 'Ask us about our off-street parking availability.', 'Call us at', 'show contact info', 'or visit us at <URL> for more information and tour options.', 'Photos are a representation of the property and may not be of the exact apartment.', '**$150 Administration Fee added to lease.', 'Pet fees/restrictions may apply.', 'Please inquire about your specific pet.', '**', 'Amenities', 'Hardwood Flooring', 'Convenient Coinless Laundry', 'Water & Trash Paid', 'Access to Clubhouse and Fitness Center', '*24 hour Emergency Maintenance', 'Online Rent Payment Portal', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 1BD/1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 600', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $957.00', 'Available:', '09/01/2022', 'Application Fee: $55.00', 'Security Deposit: $600.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs not allowed']
